OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784062068
OL,3,C'Exclusion zone' set up in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter building roof collapsed
OL,6,FAn exclusion area has been put in
OL,7,Fplace and a large police cordon set up
OL,8,Fin Leicester city centre after a
OL,9,Fbuilding roof collapsed.
OL,11,FOne person sustained minor injuries
OL,12,Fdue to the incident in Crafton Street,
OL,13,Fin the Lee Circle area, shortly after
OL,14,F7pm on Monday.
OL,16,FSeveral roads in the Wharf Street
OL,17,FSouth area were closed while emergency
OL,18,Fservices dealt with the incident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
