OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784062068
OL,3,C'Exclusion zone' set up in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter building roof collapsed
OL,6,FNearby buildings were evacuated as a
OL,7,Fprecaution while the fire service
OL,8,Fcarried out a full assessment of the
OL,9,Fdamage.
OL,11,FA police cordon remains in place in
OL,12,FWharf Street South and fencing has
OL,13,Fbeen put up to create an 'exclusion
OL,14,Farea' in the city centre.
OL,16,FDemolition signs have also been put up
OL,17,Fat the scene and several businesses
OL,18,Fremain closed today (Tuesday, July 14).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
