PN,34403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784062068
OL,3,C'Exclusion zone' set up in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter building roof collapsed
OL,6,FA statement from Leicestershire Police
OL,7,Freads: "Several roads in the Wharf
OL,8,FStreet South area of Leicester have
OL,9,Fbeen closed after a building partially
OL,10,Fcollapsed this evening (Monday 13
OL,11,FJuly).
OL,13,F"Leicestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,14,FService (LFRS) are dealing with the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,F"One person who was riding by at the
OL,18,Ftime sustained minor injuries and was
OL,19,Fdischarged by East Midlands Ambulance
OL,20,FService at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
