OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784062068
OL,3,C'Exclusion zone' set up in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter building roof collapsed
OL,6,F"In the interests of safety some
OL,7,Fnearby buildings have also been
OL,8,Fevacuated and the roads are likely to
OL,9,Fremain closed while LFRS carry out a
OL,10,Ffull assessment of the damage.
OL,12,F"We can confirm that the damage was
OL,13,Fnot caused by an explosion."
OL,15,FAn update from Leicestershire Police
OL,16,Fconfirmed the following roads remain
OL,17,Fshut:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
