PN,34405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784062068
OL,3,C'Exclusion zone' set up in Leicester
OL,4,Cafter building roof collapsed
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Leicestershire Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service said: "We received
OL,8,Fa call in relation to a roof collapse
OL,9,Fat two properties on Crafton Street
OL,10,FWest in Leicester city centre at 19:09
OL,11,Fyesterday.
OL,13,F"Crews from Central, Eastern and
OL,14,FSouthern Fire Station attended,
OL,15,Fincluding our Aerial Ladder Platform.
OL,17,F"A large amount of brickwork from the
OL,18,Ffourth story gable end had fallen into
OL,19,Fthe road, with further signs of
OL,20,Fcollapse within. A large cordon was
OL,21,Fset up around the building."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
